OL,3,CGrieving mum backs calls to seek
OL,4,Csecond opinions in hospitals
OL,6,FCalls for a Welsh equivalent of
OL,7,F'Martha's Rule' ` which allows people
OL,8,Fto seek a second medical opinion about
OL,9,Fthe care of a sick relative ` have
OL,10,Fbeen backed by a grieving mum.
OL,12,FSkyla Whiting died of sepsis in 2018
OL,13,Fwhen she was just four years old. Her
OL,14,Fmother, Amy, who lives near in , says
OL,15,Fconcerns about her daughter's
OL,16,Fcondition were ignored by medics at
OL,17,FNeville Hall hospital.
