OL,3,CGrieving mum backs calls to seek
OL,4,Csecond opinions in hospitals
OL,6,F"She became more and more unwell. She
OL,7,Fhad a raging temperature, she had a
OL,8,Frash all over her, she had an awful-
OL,9,Fsounding cough. Her temperature was up
OL,10,Fover 40.
OL,12,F"We absolutely begged for the right
OL,13,Ftreatment. We went to the nurses'
OL,14,Fstation probably 15 times through the
OL,15,Fnight."
OL,17,FAn inquest into Skyla's death two
OL,18,Fyears ago found that opportunities to
OL,19,Fsave her were missed by doctors.
