OL,3,CGrieving mum backs calls to seek
OL,4,Csecond opinions in hospitals
OL,6,FNow, Amy is backing calls to empower
OL,7,Fpatients and relatives to seek a
OL,8,Fsecond opinion in cases where they're
OL,9,Fconcerned about the deteriorating
OL,10,Fcondition of a loved one.
OL,12,FSuch a scheme ` called 'Martha's Rule'
OL,13,F` is due to be rolled out in hospitals
OL,14,Facross England next month.
OL,16,FIt would offer round-the-clock access
OL,17,Fto a rapid review from a separate care
OL,18,Fteam if someone is worried about a
OL,19,Flove one's condition.
