OL,3,CGrieving mum backs calls to seek
OL,4,Csecond opinions in hospitals
OL,6,FIt currently doesn't apply here in
OL,7,FWales, however, there is a similar
OL,8,Fservice at in .
OL,10,FThe 'Call4Concern' scheme allows adult
OL,11,Fpatients and their families to flag
OL,12,Fconcerns independently.
OL,14,FEirian Edwards, the advanced nurse
OL,15,Fpractitioner who runs the scheme, said
OL,16,Fit was proving "popular" with staff.
OL,18,F"It's a patient safety initiative. It
OL,19,Fgives our patients and relatives a
OL,20,Fvoice, and gives them an extra safety
OL,21,Fnet, really," she said.
