OL,3,CGrieving mum backs calls to seek
OL,4,Csecond opinions in hospitals
OL,6,FDr Chris Subbe, an acute physician at
OL,7,FYsbyty Gwynedd, says he gets
OL,8,Fapproximately two calls a week from
OL,9,Fworried relatives. He said some
OL,10,Fremained concerned about "dropping
OL,11,Fnurses in it."
OL,13,F"At the moment, we're conscious that
OL,14,Fnot everyone might feel that this
OL,15,Finvitation is for them, and so we
OL,16,Freally want to encourage them and say
OL,17,F'it's ok to ask,'" he said.
OL,19,FOther hospitals in Wales are expected
OL,20,Fto follow Ysbyty Gwynedd's lead.
