OL,3,CGrieving mum backs calls to seek
OL,4,Csecond opinions in hospitals
OL,6,FThe scheme has already been introduced
OL,7,Fby Cardiff and Vale University Health
OL,8,FBoard (UHB) recently.
OL,10,FBack in Torfaen, Amy says a Wales-wide
OL,11,Foffering of the service would be
OL,12,Fwelcome.
OL,14,F"We would really appreciate something
OL,15,Fsimilar to Martha's Rule, so we could
OL,16,Fget our children seen by another
OL,17,Fteam," she said.
OL,19,F"Skyla was the most beautiful girl.
OL,20,FShe had a beautiful soul."
