OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said
OL,7,Fthat Call4Concern "has seen positive
OL,8,Fsteps toward improving patient safety."
OL,10,FThey added: "We are committed to
OL,11,Fensuring the voices of patients and
OL,12,Ftheir loved ones are heard and we are
OL,13,Fworking with all NHS organisations to
OL,14,Fidentify the best patient and family-
OL,15,Finitiated escalation model to ensure
OL,16,Fimproved patient safety across all of
OL,17,Fthe NHS."
